notes: Cabaret Metro and Metro are one in the same clubs. I think sometime in the early nineties they decided to go with the shortened name of just Metro.
There was a tape flip between Been A Son and Negative Creep but nothing was cut, so I simply merged the wav forms. I suppose if someone wants to, you could
crossfade the wavs and produce a less noticeable split, but I just left the recording as is. Enjoy.
